{"commentv2": 1, "number": 46, "id": 600515, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Shadowswift", "body": "If I'm a Night Elf Warrior, someone who has nor wants anything to do with magic, why does Maly want me dead? Was it something I said? :(", "date": "2009-02-08T14:13:49-06:00", "rating": 24, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "probably he didnt sleep good that night, and he was a bit pist off", "creationdate": "2009-04-19T13:07:56-05:00", "id": 92386, "rating": 10, "commentid": 600515, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "barthem", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 47, "id": 612143, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Reunilana", "body": "Known bugs in  Patch 3.0.8\r\nA) He will hit random players in phase 1 even if they dont have aggro\r\nB) He can instant turn 180 degres and cast breath on raid even if tank has 100% aggro\r\nC) Pets can bug boss and also they get bugged themself when wortex\r\nD) http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=48088 and http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=53251  doesnt work any more\r\nE) Phase 3 background is terible for looking", "date": "2009-02-16T18:17:08-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 48, "id": 613801, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "254148", "body": "Has anyone else noticed that you're able in some cases to zone into the fight during phase 3? I've been able to reproduce it sometimes and think that you either have to release during phase 3 or re-enter as a ghost during phase 3 (releasing and re-entering during phase 2 gives you back your body and makes you unable to zone in until malygos is killed or despawns). I got a drake right as he despawned earlier tonight and managed to fight him in phase 1 on it, doing a whopping 13.5k dps with double-stacked ticks of 20+ stacks of the dot hitting for around 100k.", "date": "2009-02-18T01:57:52-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
