{"commentv2": 1, "number": 51, "id": 625627, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Magnett", "body": "Best. Voice acting. Ever. I just wish I could stop picturing Medivh and Liquid Snake whenever I hear one of his quotes.\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_Prefight01.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Lesser beings, intruding here! A shame that your excess courage does not compensate for your stupidity!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_Prefight02.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"None but the blue dragonflight are welcome here! Perhaps this is the work of Alexstrasza? Well then, she has sent you to your deaths.\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_Prefight03.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"What could you hope to accomplish... to storm brazenly into my domain? To employ magic? Against me? Hahahahaha!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_Prefight04.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"I am without limits here...the rules of your cherished reality do not apply. In this realm, I am in control!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_Prefight05.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"I give you one chance. Pledge fealty to me, and perhaps I won't slaughter you for your insolence!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_AggroPhase1.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"My patience has reached its limit. I will be rid of you!\"[/i] \n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_AggroPhase2.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Few have experienced the pain I will now inflict on you!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_AggroPhase3.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Submit!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_EndPhase01.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"I had hoped to end your lives quickly, but you have proven more... resilient then I had anticipated. Nonetheless, your efforts are in vain. It is you reckless, careless mortals who are to blame for this war! I do what I must... and if it means your... extinction... then so be it!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_EndPhase02.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Enough! If you intend to reclaim Azeroth's magic, then you shall have it.\"[/i] \n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_IntroPhase3.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Now your benefactors make their appearance, but they are too late. The powers contained here are powerful enough to destroy the world ten times over! What do you think they will do to you?\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_BreathAttack.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"You will not succeed while I draw breath!\"[/i] \n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_GenericSpell01.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Still standing? Not for long...\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_GenericSpell02.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Your cause is lost!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_GenericSpell03.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Your fragile mind will be shattered!\"[/i] \n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_BigAtttackPhase3.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"The powers at work here exceed anything you could possibly imagine!\"[/i] \n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_AntiMagicShell.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"I will teach you ignorant children just how little you know of magic...\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_MagicBlast.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Watch helplessly as your hopes are swept away!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_HighDamageMode.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"I am unstoppable!\"[/i] \n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase1-01.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Your stupidity has finally caught up with you!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase1-02.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"More artifacts to confiscate...\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase1-03.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Hahaha! How very... na\u00efve.\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase2-01.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Your energy will be put to good use!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase2-02.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"I am the spell-weaver! My power is infinite!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase2-03.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Your spirit will linger here forever!\"[/i] \n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase3-01.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Alexstrasza! Another of your brood falls!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase3-02.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Little more than gnats!\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_SlayPhase3-03.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Your red allies will share your fate.\"[/i]\n\n[b]/script PlaySoundFile(\"Sound\\\\Creature\\\\Malygos\\\\EE_Malygos_Death01.wav\")[/b]\n[i]\"Unthinkable! The mortals will destroy... everything! My sister... what have you...\"[/i]", "date": "2009-02-27T19:43:58-06:00", "rating": 29, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "For anyone wondering why these no longer work, replace the extension (.wav) to .ogg", "creationdate": "2015-12-17T16:36:44-06:00", "id": 919045, "rating": 1, "commentid": 625627, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "stathisdjs", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-02-27T19:44:39-06:00", 1, "Magnett"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 52, "id": 634043, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Tripix", "body": "There are many confuses about this spell. While fighting with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=28859]Malygos[/url] best way to deal with healing is assign two players on normal and four or five for heroic for AoE heals only. Easiest way to heal is keeping 5 stacks of Revivify on themselfs, stack 5 combo points (by spamming Revivify on self) and then cast Life Burst.\n\n[b]About Life Burst:[/b]\n[ul]\n  [li][b]It doesn't heal over time[/b], it is just a one big AoE heal.[/li]\n  [li]The more combo points you stack the bigger heal is.[/li]\n  [li]The more combo points you stack the 50% healing buff last longer.[/li]\n  [li]50% healing buff work for both - [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=57143]Life Burst[/url] and [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=57090]Revivify[/url][/li]\n[/ul]\n\nIt's good, but not essentially if dps dragons try to hold 1-2 (or more) stacks of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=57090]Revivify[/url]. And most major issue is to all drakes stay close to themselfs. They should stay in one big group, and when Malygos cast  AoE spell they should all move a bit. Good way to have proper position is to stick to clock hours (12 - 9 - 6 - 3 etc).", "date": "2009-03-07T05:59:43-06:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-03-12T19:56:52-05:00", 2, "Tripix"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 53, "id": 639937, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "LatroVir", "body": "Malygos is voiced by [url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0164682/]Cam Clarke[/url], whom you may have noticed voices a few other characters in World of Warcraft as well... Namely the Last Guardian [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=15608]Medivh[/url], and the Player Blood Elf Male voice.\r\n\r\nTwo noteworthy voice overs that this VA has done outside WoW would be Liquid Snake for the Metal Gear Solid Series... and also Prince Adam/He-man, which this game also makes a reference to with the AB Battlemaster [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=20273]Adam Eternum[/url].", "date": "2009-03-12T11:36:34-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 54, "id": 659609, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "leonheart87", "body": "Malygos is a strange fellow. Seeks to destroy all mortal life for fear they will use magic in a bad way, yet he allows his followers (the scions in phase 2, some in the Azure Dragonshrine) to use magic. \r\n\r\nUnless they are another breed of elf, which hasn't lost it's immortality, he is going against everything he was fighting for. Maybe, he has so much power, he can give them immortality and they're just high/blood elves.\r\n\r\nWonder who will replace him as the ruler of the Blue Dragonflight, can't be many Blue Dragons left, we seem to kill alot of them. [url=http://www.wowwiki.com/Blue_dragonflight]Wowwiki[/url] only lists 6 as being alive, with 1 whelp.", "date": "2009-03-29T16:33:22-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 55, "id": 661543, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "343793", "body": "Button-jammers of the world rejoice.  For the rest of us, this encounter is hell.  Have your therapist's number handy.", "date": "2009-03-31T11:31:06-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 56, "id": 673082, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "39022", "body": "Until patch 3.1 goes live http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=53601#comments:id=673080 will still be extremely useful on the Malygos fight.  Right before vortex I make sure to have Sacred Shield on everyone in the raid (10m version).  It will proc 2x during the vortex for approx. a 4-5k dmg absorption to everyone.  Combined with 2-4 heals available (2 holy shocks, 2 proc'd instant flash of lights) and using your beacon of light intelligently, a holy paladin is a great healer for malygos.  I see many ppl claim that they are useless for that fight, well those ppl have no knowledge of the class.  Flash of light can sometimes be forced to cast during the vortex if you can proc a boost of haste from trinkets such as http://www.wowhead.com/?item=40685.  \r\n\r\nWhen 3.1 hits pally's will become very boring healers.  Only being able to cast this on the tank will take away most of our strategy when raid healing other than beacon swapping and stacking everyone up for http://www.wowhead.com/?item=41106.  IMO in 3.1 they should reduce the mana cost of http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=53563.  This will bring the strategy back to healing as a paladin.", "date": "2009-04-11T15:03:10-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "More to the point, as a paladin healer, when Malygos is getting ready to do his Vortex thing.... [ol][li]Use your [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=31842]Divine Illumination[/url] if it is up.  You're about to burn a lot of mana.[/li] [li]Put [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=53563]Beacon of Light[/url] on [i]yourself[/i], since you can guarantee that you will be in range for it.[/li] [li]Put [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?spell=53601]Sacred Shield[/url] on [s]every low-health target you can[/s] one low-health target.  Priests are often very squishy and should usually be prioritized.[/li] [li]", "creationdate": "2009-04-11T15:03:11-05:00", "id": 399430, "rating": 2, "commentid": 673082, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Kathucka", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 57, "id": 676373, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Rattja", "body": "There seem to be a bug in the second phase, he seem to sometimes come down and start attacking the raid with melee.\nThis wiped us today, and I wonder. Do anyone know what triggers this, or why it happens?\nOh and you can't target him so tanking him threw this bug, or whatever you want to call it, is impossible.\n\n*Edit* This happened twice, again, for no reason, Malygos comes down and start to melee everyone according to the threat list from the first phase... Hope this get fixed in the upcoming patch", "date": "2009-04-14T16:17:24-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-04-14T16:25:34-05:00", 1, "Rattja"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 58, "id": 696687, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "358069", "body": "[i][b]\"I had hoped to end your lives quickly, but you have proven more... resilient than I anticipated.  Nonetheless, your efforts are in vain.  It it you reckless, careless mortals who are to blame for this war!  I do what I must, and if it means your extinction... THEN SO BE IT!\"\n\n\"Lesser beings, intruding here!  A shame that your excess courage does not compensate for your stupidity!\n\n\"The power contained here is enough to destroy the world ten times over!  What do you think it will do to you?\"[/b][/i]\n\nThose three quotes are possibly the most badass quotes in the entire game, in my opinion.", "date": "2009-04-27T18:56:44-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-04-27T18:59:06-05:00", 2, "358069"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 59, "id": 697948, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Darthmrkew", "body": "I am very sad what happened to all aspects.\r\nNozdormu betrayed.\r\nNeltharion betrayed.\r\nMalygos betrayed.\r\nYsera is sleeping.\r\nAlexstrasza didn't prevent what happened at wrathgate.", "date": "2009-04-28T18:52:16-05:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "You don\u00b4t have all true.....   Neltharion is pure evil, destroyer he betray everyone at WotA when he turn into madness.(he turn mad cuz old god had him as woodo doll). Nozdormu is a poor guy and he had eyes only for his repertory of monuments and he have head in sand . Malygos try to stop mortal races from bad using of magic....for good of world (mean dont \"call \" Burning Legion again) but Alexstrazsa had gift a promise to Rhonin at day of dragon (the red dragonflight will help at everytime as it posiblle same against other flight.....so she decided to stop Malygos and defeat him........ Yser", "creationdate": "2009-04-28T18:52:17-05:00", "id": 468554, "rating": -1, "commentid": 697948, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Zultian", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "WHAT?  Nozdormu NEVER betrayed Azeroth (Even now he tries to save it...for that reason he hires heroes to restore fractured timeline", "creationdate": "2010-01-14T14:16:09-06:00", "id": 143294, "rating": 0, "commentid": 697948, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Daralyn", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Unless you subscribe to the theory that Nozdormu is behind the Infinite Dragonflight.  Between the novels (apologizes to Korial for the future) and some of the quests in WOTLK (chromie quests and the bronze in CoS getting turned into an infinite) there are some clues that could be interpreted that way.    See [url=http://www.wowwiki.com/Infinite_dragonflight]wowwiki[/url].", "creationdate": "2010-01-20T09:29:54-06:00", "id": 144346, "rating": 1, "commentid": 697948, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "valorum", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
