{"commentv2": 1, "number": 82, "id": 1149481, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "609114", "body": "Today in an attempt he reset to 100% health after phase 2. I'm sure this is not intended. I've heard other people reporting this.\r\n\r\nEdit: Why downrank? This is a bug, people should be aware of it.", "date": "2010-10-21T13:51:14-05:00", "rating": 32, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "same issue on french servers, try 16 times since Wednesday and life is between 70 and 100% in phase 3 some groups manage to kill him because life doesn't reset, perhaps too much damage in phase 2", "creationdate": "2010-10-22T11:05:23-05:00", "id": 188082, "rating": 8, "commentid": 1149481, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "243276", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2010-10-25T11:07:27-05:00", 1, "609114"]}
