{"commentv2": 1, "number": 139, "id": 1845405, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "1051034", "body": "Soloed him on my ilvl 504 rogue.  Phase three was the hardest, and it took a few tries to kill him.  But I did it.  No mount, but now I know I can do it.\n\nEdit: 10 days later, on May 1st, I got [item=43952], on my third trip soloing it.  Now for the blue one...\n\nEdit 2: 13 days after getting [item=43952], I got [item=43953].  My ilvl now is 508", "date": "2013-04-21T02:55:27-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2013-05-14T05:14:40-05:00", 3, "1051034"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 140, "id": 1846286, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Atrisha", "body": "Just solo'd him as a 489 Shadow Priest. For those having a hard time in phase 3 I can confirm that 1,1,2,3 does work, you just can't rush it. It took me 8 times to finally kill him because I was frantically button smashing. Once I slowed down and took my time I downed him easily. Plus the blue drake dropped for me the first time! Will keep doing this until I get the azure drake as well.", "date": "2013-04-23T15:41:47-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
