{"commentv2": 1, "number": 142, "id": 1857672, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Bowserkills7", "body": "Currently having an issue where I lag spiked in the middle of a Lightning Storm during drake phase and died, while my dot ticked over and killed Malygos.\r\n\r\nWhenever I try to spawn into the instance, I just fall down to my death. Anyone else had this issue?", "date": "2013-05-25T10:00:08-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 143, "id": 1857758, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "rehlyihmah", "body": "I don't know if anyone posted this before (or if it is alright to do this in the first place, though I don't think this is an exploit), but...\r\n\r\nI soloed him today in 25 man mode without any sort of enrage time pressure.\r\n\r\nPhase 1: Nuke as much as you can. It doesn't really matter how far down you get his HP, but it makes phase 3 a little less annoying. As an 522 Elemental Shaman I got him down to ~45-50%.\r\n\r\nPhase 2: Kill all Adds except for one. If you've got some passive effect dealing damage to attackers - i.e. Lightning Shield - remove it. Stay on your flying disk thingie. Wait. Waiting is the most important part of this phase, for you a) wait until Malygos enrages (he cannot kill you in this phase) and b) wait until his Berserker is over. That takes 30 minutes, so do this if you, I don't know, want to cook lunch and meanwhile do something \"meaningful\" in WoW. Once the 30 minutes are over, kill the last add and have fun in...\r\n\r\nPhase 3: I personally use 3-3-3-3-3-1-1-1-1-1-2-1-1-1-1-1-2-3-3-3-3-3 and so on. Maybe 4 with 5 stacks of 1 if I drop low from, I don't know, chatting in the guild channel and not moving out of something quickly enough. \r\n\r\nAll in all, it was completely pointless with both drakes dropping in 10 man and took 45 minutes. I didn't have to ask for help, though, so, whatever. xD", "date": "2013-05-25T13:52:52-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Yep, this works. Tedious and mostly pointless, but at least I can say I soloed it on 25 man. One other thing to note, though, is that the last enemy in phase 2 will keep attacking you - it'll miss most of the time, but it was hitting me for ~16k when it connected, which adds up after a while. So make sure to keep an eye on your health while you're waiting.", "creationdate": "2013-06-03T16:23:28-05:00", "id": 665787, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1857758, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "voodoopimp", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
