{"commentv2": 1, "number": 146, "id": 1863782, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "319936", "body": "The Dragon Aspects:\n[ul]\n[li][b]Bronze[/b]: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/hearthstone/card=411&image&notip]Nozdormu[/url] the Timeless One[/li]\n[li][b]Red[/b]: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/hearthstone/card=581&image&notip]Alexstrasza[/url] the Life-Binder[/li]\n[li][b][url=http://www.wowhead.com/hearthstone/card=489&image&notip]Green[/url][/b]: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/hearthstone/card=1186&image&notip]Ysera[/url] the Dreamer (former); the Awakened (present).[/li]\n[li][b][url=http://www.wowhead.com/hearthstone/card=825&image&notip]Blue[/url][/b]: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/hearthstone/card=436&image&notip]Malygos[/url] the Spell-Weaver (former); [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=38017]Kalecgos[/url] the Steward of Magic (present)[/li]\n[li][b]Black[/b]: [url=http://www.wowhead.com/hearthstone/card=834&image&notip]Neltharion[/url] the Earth Warder (former); Deathwing the Destroyer (recent)[/li]\n[/ul]", "date": "2013-06-07T07:22:50-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2013-06-10T21:31:07-05:00", 2, "319936"]}
