{"commentv2": 1, "number": 150, "id": 1884439, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "GDerkon", "body": "Some things I've discovered.. A may prove useful..\r\n\r\n1... No matter what side you are.. using the transport to Borean Tundra is the best way to get to the Raid.. Flying from Dalaran may seem a good idea, but.. its not..\r\n\r\n2. Any class can kill him.. if you re 90.. and with a ilvl as much as 430 you can down him.. I recomend full crafted pvp gear..\r\n\r\n3. Its possible to alter the rotation to 1 1 1 2 3. Malygos dies far more faster.\r\n\r\n4. Up vote the guys who came with the idea of that rotation.\r\n\r\n5. Dont give up.. BOTH mount do drop from this guy.\r\n\r\nHave fun above else! ...\r\n\r\nCheers :)", "date": "2013-08-06T05:32:20-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I dont think more 1 add up dmg, they just add up time of the dot. Today i got both mounts from Eye of Eternity 10 man so they deffinetly drop.", "creationdate": "2013-08-12T10:15:39-05:00", "id": 684369, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1884439, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Mikiti", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
