{"commentv2": 1, "number": 153, "id": 1912810, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Kaleb", "body": "i would like to mention that while malygos is talking you can still damage him and get him real low. Just make sure not to kill him before the dragon phase. I'm not sure if it would bug him, but better to be safe than sorry.", "date": "2013-10-28T13:37:43-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "It's actually fine to keep DPSing him, he will stop taking damage at 1hp in phase one. Then once phase 3 begins, you can hit him with one spell to finish him off.", "creationdate": "2013-11-03T17:34:00-06:00", "id": 705632, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1912810, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "fiveofeight", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2013-11-23T17:57:49-06:00", 1, "Kaleb"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 154, "id": 1920828, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "1196281", "body": "this might not be read. but i encountered a bug of sorts. i soloed malygos and missed the rage timer by roughly three seconds. i was killed but my dot tick ended up finishing him up right after. as i respawned and entered the raid i would not mount the drakes rather just fell and died. this happened two times. third time the drakes caught me but the loot chest only gave me like 17 gold. anyone else hit this issue?", "date": "2013-11-24T05:31:05-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 16384, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 155, "id": 1922623, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "zeiz", "body": "Tried this today at 10 man as ilvl 540 frost DK. Used crystal of insanity + strength food, popped army and went full out on him. he ended up on 25% HP in phase 1 and phase 2 I obviosly died since I could barely damage him alone.\r\n\r\nWill try again when I have atleast 560 ilvl. So to sum it up, BEWARE, this boss is REALLY hard to solo atleast as DK.", "date": "2013-12-01T07:59:29-06:00", "rating": -6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Lol, this boss is stupidly easy to solo, I even did it on 25m and I have a lower iLvl than you. You sure you're doing 1-1-2-3 rotation on the drake?", "creationdate": "2014-02-06T09:27:17-06:00", "id": 726846, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1922623, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "BscorpobBx5", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Also make sure you keep moving while on the drake in phase 3. If you just sat there and spammed the first ability, of course you're going to fail.", "creationdate": "2014-03-02T05:29:31-06:00", "id": 732318, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1922623, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Fir3shadow", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "zeiz, you must be don't something wrong then, because this boss should be an absolute cake walk with ilvl 540 gear. Phase 1: Blow cooldowns and do as much damage as you can. Just before phase 1 ends, refresh dots, and when Malygos flies up, used any ranged damage you can. Phase 2: Kill adds. Phase 3: Use rotation 1,1,2,3. Avoid the aoe damage. Job done. It's not hard.", "creationdate": "2014-03-16T08:10:19-05:00", "id": 735012, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1922623, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "sbowesuk", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
