{"commentv2": 1, "number": 173, "id": 2060185, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Elanorien", "body": "Can confirm that as of December 2014 Malygos DOES drop both the Blue and the Azure Drake.  I farmed and EoE 10m Normal and got the Azure Drake during MoP and today, when reading people were getting the Blue Drake as a drop I decided to go for it.  Killed Malygos on 5 toons, 10m Normal, in one sitting today; Azure dropped on the third and (as others have said happened to them) BOTH dropped on the 5th.  So they must have increased the drop rate because that was a piece of cake.\r\n\r\nI've wanted the Blue Drake since Malygos was current but never saw him drop, so I was insanely excited.  Not to mention I've always thought, since Wrath, that they should've had a a green drake in the game.  Blue was the last I needed for the Awake the Drakes achievement so now I have TWO drakes that I've desperately wanted for many years XD.\r\n\r\nThey were pretty easy kills even on my mediocre geared level 90s (two of them being tanks in tank gear and spec).", "date": "2014-12-05T09:27:33-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
