{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 710699, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "236163", "body": "This is an [url=http://images2.wikia.nocookie.net/wowwiki/images/4/42/YoggMalygos.jpg]image[/url] of Malygos projected by Yogg-Saron during his encounter in Ulduar. \r\n\r\nThe scene reacted here is the creation of the Demon Soul in the hands of Deathwing during a meeting of the dragon aspects in the Wyrmrest Accord.\r\n\r\nOther new faces found in the meeting are [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=33495]Ysera[/url] and of course [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=33523]Neltharion/Deathwing[/url] himself, each using a mortal disguise.", "date": "2009-05-09T13:13:27-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 711493, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "167903", "body": "The Aspect's Mortal Forms : \r\n\r\nYsera <The Dreamer : Night Elf Female\r\nNeltharion <The Earthwarder> : Human Male\r\nMalygos <The Spellweaver> : High Elf Male\r\n\r\nEven though Alexstrasza(<The Lifebinder>) isn't here, her model is either a High Elf or a Blood Elf", "date": "2009-05-10T06:30:47-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Alexstrasza's mortal guise is something... resembling an elf, sort of, but clearly she's taken it upon herself to take a further step in creating a unique mortal guise.  She can be seen at the top of Wyrmrest Temple in Dragonblight in this mortal form. http://www.wowhead.com/?npc=26917", "creationdate": "2009-07-03T02:27:33-05:00", "id": 107431, "rating": 1, "commentid": 711493, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "shiftingillusion", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
