{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 369460, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "143549", "body": "If he were killed, the ties to the magical plain would be cut, making the only playable classes the ones not using magic (e.g. Warriors, Rogues...).\r\n\r\nObviously this would run into problems with the environment too (e.g. [url=http://wotlk.wowhead.com/?zone=4395]Dalaran[/url] would crash to the earth due to no magic, the Wards protecting [url=http://wotlk.wowhead.com/?zone=4080]Isle of Quel'danas[/url] and [url=http://wotlk.wowhead.com/?zone=3487]Silvermoon[/url] etc. would not work...)\r\n\r\nPlease Correct me if I have made a mistake somewhere (dead link etc.)", "date": "2008-09-05T14:03:48-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "magic does noet exist in the world because of malygos, he was just granted vast power over it by the titans...", "creationdate": "2008-09-07T15:25:36-05:00", "id": 348961, "rating": 1, "commentid": 369460, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "hagelslag", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "True to an extent, though priests and paladins use the light, shaman use nature and druids use nature aswell.  So the classes that would suffer would be mages, and warlocks, seeing as warlocks are corrupted (powerhungry etc) mages. A caster class does not mean a magic class perse. :)", "creationdate": "2009-04-04T19:11:07-05:00", "id": 89393, "rating": 0, "commentid": 369460, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "2OfDiamonds", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Sure, but in essence its still magic.", "creationdate": "2009-05-17T04:49:47-05:00", "id": 98449, "rating": 2, "commentid": 369460, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "81339", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "not all warlocks would suffer without magic, as the orc warlocks are corrupted shamans", "creationdate": "2010-05-29T11:07:05-05:00", "id": 165717, "rating": 2, "commentid": 369460, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Rasmushansen", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
