{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 479598, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "MalygosHelper", "body": "Malygos was once and he is stil, a protector. Even the Red Dragonflight says that magic was going to destroy the world and the Aspects were going to have a meeting about this. Malygos instead of the meeting, declared war on every spellcaster. His reasons are good ones, only the methods [i]may be considered[/i] wrong\n\nAnd about the magic issue: he is declaring war against the reckless use of [u]Arcane Magic[/u]. It may really produce cataclysms. www.wowpedia.org/Arcane_Magic", "date": "2008-11-30T04:09:30-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Well, he wouldn't risk trying to speak with all the races of Azeroth. We're too busy with our petty conflicts to listen to a Protector. I read that Black dragons were the most violent and dangerous dragons of all. Apparentlly, Malygos is \"borrowing\" a tactic from them: \"Whoever comes within 50 meters of me is going to be engulfed in a sheet of fire and torn to shreds\".", "creationdate": "2008-12-24T21:23:11-06:00", "id": 67491, "rating": 1, "commentid": 479598, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "289089", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-02-13T14:29:33-06:00", 2, "MalygosHelper"]}
