{"commentv2": 1, "number": 22, "id": 1334790, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "MalygosHelper", "body": "Claiming his actions to be wrong is a bit... excessive. \nMalygos has made wise decisions in past, and those decisions were a product not of insanity, but likely the opposite, of geniality ( if we don't talk about supporting Deathwing with the Demon Soul). Algalon himself wanted to destroy Azeroth too. And he is the ambassador of the makers. \nNow, maybe [b]we[/b] are the bad guys. The mortals races after all have caused so many conflicts (Sundering, <Malygos Insanity> and... Whoot, Kael'thas betrays his own people, attempting to summon the Legion for the second time, then comes the Nexus War)... And i don't really think the Kirin Tor knowledge would overcome the Blue Dragonflight's one. The Alliance and the Horde have always been blind, in these times. But i am not keen of how Blizzard attempts to justify the killing of all bosses. In vanilla it wasn't so, at all (just look at Azuregos).", "date": "2011-02-13T14:23:14-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The Northrend expedition made me somewhat uncomfortable.  The idea of ending the reign of the Lich King made sense for the overall good of Azeroth for the scourge were a plague on it.  In addition Arthas was a human and in his fallibility he made decisions which effected the other mortal races as well as Azeroth as a whole, therefore it was appropriate for the mortal races to intervene and stop the Lich King.  Malygos, however did not have the same feeble view of the world as Arthas or in fact the leaders of Dalaran.  Therefore the Wyrmrest Accord not the Kirin Tor should have completely orche", "creationdate": "2011-02-13T14:23:15-06:00", "id": 483581, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1334790, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "630009", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-02-13T14:24:47-06:00", 1, "MalygosHelper"]}
